    "name": "No Vacation for an Executioner Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3150270,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150270/extras/render_460x215.png?t=1753147854\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a story about a frustrated executioner in late 17th century. He felt sick at his job and ran away from the gallows. It aroused a riot of monsters, he had to clean up this cruel mess, and find out the truth about the &quot;Gloomy Oil&quot; of this crazy world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a retro PS2 style Dark Fantasy Action-RPG, you will use various skill to knock down your enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the Book : The Hangman of Paris by Claude Cueni, and the Paintings of Zdzisław Beksiński. (But it's a story nothing about any Sanson family)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique art style</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special art style makes you immerse into the nightmare of executioner. Half sketch half real rendering a different kind of Baroque times.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150270/extras/e249f43899ba3ca392c18411de61ca53.avif?t=1753147854\" width=460 height=351 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Different battle system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fighting straightly will make the battle very tough. It will be much better to use any skills, like BACKSTAB or PARRY, and use your gun properly. Grow up and reinforce your gears through the battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150270/extras/57e33bfbb63a7001162f063e379cb263.avif?t=1753147854\" width=460 height=301 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Attire system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various attires and hats can be changed, they also have different functions. Update your outfit and catch the fashion of early 18th century.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150270/extras/e2db5d6c2717c2976642d41e4376cdde.avif?t=1753147854\" width=460 height=330 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Item transfer system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Item Craft System. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect different items on the road and transfer them into valuable resource, like different kinds of bullets or herbs for example.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150270/extras/56923de7b1ac370d8aa2ec1e80078d9d.avif?t=1753147854\" width=460 height=304 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150270/extras/17b78c8ebb9e2dc4ec8f7cf64254767d.avif?t=1753147854\" width=460 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150270/extras/85cfc64968498091741757b3ceb7b573.poster.avif?t=1753147854\" width=360 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150270/extras/85cfc64968498091741757b3ceb7b573.webm?t=1753147854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150270/extras/85cfc64968498091741757b3ceb7b573.mp4?t=1753147854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
